00:41:50,660 --> 00:41:51,380
 tvoje mišljenje.

1193
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:52,600
 Onda se ne moramo

1194
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:53,500
 ni mi kao Hrvatska

1195
00:41:53,500 --> 00:41:54,980
 gurat negdje i davat komentare

1196
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:56,020
 ni tipa Plenkovića,

1197
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:57,040
 ni tipa Milanovića.

1198
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:57,560
 Je, je, slažno.

1199
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:58,840
 Ajmo brinuti o sebi.

1200
00:41:58,840 --> 00:42:00,480
 Prvenstvene osobi, slažno.

1201
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,460
 Jer, vidiš da se svi oni se povuku,

1202
00:42:02,460 --> 00:42:03,460
 šta ćemo sad mi ostati?

1203
00:42:03,460 --> 00:42:04,200
 Mali, statistička povješka.

1204
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:05,400
 Mi po tom pitanju,

1205
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,520
 kažem, ne bi,

1206
00:42:06,520 --> 00:42:07,600
 treba bi gledati prvenstveno

1207
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:08,800
 svoj interes i to je to.

1208
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:10,140
 Recimo Ukrajina,

1209
00:42:10,140 --> 00:42:10,900
 već možda pričati

1210
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:12,220
 i mi imamo neki svoj interes.

1211
00:42:12,220 --> 00:42:13,900
 To se radi o našoj regiji i tako dalje.

1212
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,080
 neko dugoročno jase,

1213
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:16,880
 založen za neke stvaranje

1214
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:19,780
 nekog savjeza

1215
00:42:19,780 --> 00:42:23,080
 između tri umora,

1216
00:42:23,080 --> 00:42:24,420
 Jadram Baltic, Crno more,

1217
00:42:24,420 --> 00:42:25,880
 to su zemlje s kojima dijelimo

1218
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,920
 i na neki način

1219
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:29,680
 neku sudbinu, povijest,

1220
00:42:29,680 --> 00:42:32,740
 pa i geopolitičke

1221
00:42:32,740 --> 00:42:33,860
 i gospodarske interese

1222
00:42:33,860 --> 00:42:36,200
 i tu je Ukrajina veliki ovaj faktor.

1223
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,780
 Međutim, okolo ovoga,

1224
00:42:37,780 --> 00:42:39,540
 mi ih pogotovo kao Hrvatska,

1225
00:42:39,540 --> 00:42:41,220
 ja, tu ne možemo,

1226
00:42:41,220 --> 00:42:42,820
 mi možemo ovako tu komentirati

1227
00:42:42,820 --> 00:42:43,420
 i tako dalje.

1228
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,420
 Međutim, ne trebamo se tu previše.

1229
00:42:45,420 --> 00:42:48,020
 To je isto moje mišljenje.

1230
00:42:48,020 --> 00:42:52,680
 Odnosi Hrvatski sa Srbijom.

1231
00:42:52,680 --> 00:42:55,120
 Predsjednik Srbije je nemiruje.

1232
00:42:55,120 --> 00:42:56,420
 Dobili su Zagrebčanku,

1233
00:42:56,420 --> 00:42:58,120
 tako zvanu.

1234
00:42:58,120 --> 00:43:00,420
 Je, je, počeli su oboružavanca

1235
00:43:00,420 --> 00:43:01,780
 sa raketama.

1236
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:02,900
 Da li je to njegov način da ostane tamo na vlasti?

1237
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:03,560
 Pa ja mislim da je.

1238
00:43:03,560 --> 00:43:06,460
 Jer Srbija je postala jedan veliki

1239
00:43:06,460 --> 00:43:08,560
 šov,

1240
00:43:08,560 --> 00:43:10,600
 zadruga je njihov

1241
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:12,920
 slike i prilika.

1242
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:15,260
 da stanja u Srbiji,

1243
00:43:15,260 --> 00:43:16,260
 to je jedan veliki,

1244
00:43:16,260 --> 00:43:17,100
 kako se to kaže,

1245
00:43:17,100 --> 00:43:21,100
 žanr,

1246
00:43:21,100 --> 00:43:25,520
 tabloidi i tako dalje.

1247
00:43:25,520 --> 00:43:26,340
 Žuta štamba.

1248
00:43:26,340 --> 00:43:26,940
 Žuta štamba.

1249
00:43:26,940 --> 00:43:27,800
 Ma ne, ono,

1250
00:43:27,800 --> 00:43:29,100
 uglavnom, ono,

1251
00:43:29,100 --> 00:43:30,340
 Srbiji je sve šov,

1252
00:43:30,340 --> 00:43:31,400
 sve spektakali,

1253
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:32,020
 tako onda,

1254
00:43:32,020 --> 00:43:33,620
 da bi ostale na vlasti,

1255
00:43:33,620 --> 00:43:34,760
 morate dajte spektakali,

1256
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:36,240
 ne prijatelje od onih koji vam,

1257
00:43:36,240 --> 00:43:38,060
 okej, mi je,

1258
00:43:38,060 --> 00:43:39,720
 imamo povijeska koju imamo,

1259
00:43:39,720 --> 00:43:40,480
 međutim,

1260
00:43:40,480 --> 00:43:42,540
 da sad prijeti neki sukob,

1261
00:43:42,540 --> 00:43:43,920
 naravno da ne.

1262
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:45,260
 Mi smo to,

1263
00:43:45,260 --> 00:43:46,460
 ja se bar nadam,

1264
00:43:46,460 --> 00:43:46,900
 riješili,

1265
00:43:46,900 --> 00:43:47,180
 eto,

1266
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:47,960
 prijatelje,

1267
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:48,440
 prijatelje.

1268
00:43:48,440 --> 00:43:50,260
 On kaže da je to zbog onog saveza,

1269
00:43:50,260 --> 00:43:51,960
 Priština, Tirana, Zagreb.

1270
00:43:51,960 --> 00:43:52,540
 Da, je, da.

1271
00:43:52,540 --> 00:43:53,900
 Savez koji nije,

1272
00:43:53,900 --> 00:43:55,500
 savez koji nije savez,

1273
00:43:55,500 --> 00:43:57,920
 neko je suradnja, jel da?

1274
00:43:57,920 --> 00:43:58,260
 Mislim,

1275
00:43:58,260 --> 00:44:00,640
 imamo određene suradnje i sa Srbijom,

1276
00:44:00,640 --> 00:44:02,220
 pisanje prije negdje 15-a godina.

1277
00:44:02,220 --> 00:44:03,300
 Da, već dugo i vojnu tako su.

1278
00:44:03,300 --> 00:44:04,660
 Da, vojnu suradnju,

1279
00:44:04,660 --> 00:44:06,760
 imamo vojnu suradnju i sa njima,

1280
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:08,320
 ali to iz njihove,

1281
00:44:08,320 --> 00:44:11,020
 iz Vučićeve PR perspektive zvuči

1282
00:44:11,020 --> 00:44:11,600
 jako dobro,

1283
00:44:11,700 --> 00:44:13,880
 pogotovo za njegovu glasaču gubazu,

1284
00:44:13,880 --> 00:44:15,480
 koja je to starija i tako dalje,

1285
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:16,080
 koja ono,

1286
00:44:16,080 --> 00:44:18,380
 i dalje živi u tom nekim bajkama

1287
00:44:18,380 --> 00:44:20,880
 o krvočnim ustašama i tako dalje,

1288
00:44:20,880 --> 00:44:21,720
 tako da,

1289
00:44:21,720 --> 00:44:24,760
 s te perspektive mogu razumijet,

1290
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:25,540
 u smislu, znam,

1291
00:44:25,540 --> 00:44:26,620
 očito je to,

1292
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:29,620
 to neki razlog zašto se to događa.

1293
00:44:29,620 --> 00:44:31,140
 Međutim, eto.

1294
00:44:31,140 --> 00:44:32,940
 Ali moram priznati da,

1295
00:44:32,940 --> 00:44:35,120
 recimo i njemu i plenku i čupašu

1296
00:44:35,120 --> 00:44:36,060
 ovi svjetski sukobi,

1297
00:44:36,060 --> 00:44:38,240
 jer tad se vlast redko mijenja.

1298
00:44:38,240 --> 00:44:39,320
 Je, je, upravo to.

1299
00:44:39,320 --> 00:44:39,960
 Je, je.

1300
00:44:39,960 --> 00:44:41,280
 Tad se vlast redko mijenja

1301
00:44:41,280 --> 00:44:42,880
 i njima je dobro.

1302
00:44:42,880 --> 00:44:43,440
 Je.

1303
00:44:43,440 --> 00:44:46,000
 Kakao je plan hrvatskih suveriste dalje

1304
00:44:46,000 --> 00:44:46,980
 za cijelu hrvatsku?

1305
00:44:46,980 --> 00:44:48,160
 Podružnice,

1306
00:44:48,160 --> 00:44:49,380
 jačanje, vjerovatno,

1307
00:44:49,380 --> 00:44:49,880
 tako.

1308
00:44:49,880 --> 00:44:50,600
 Pa je.

1309
00:44:50,600 --> 00:44:51,620
 Okupljanje desnici,

1310
00:44:51,620 --> 00:44:53,040
 da smo rekli na početku, da.

1311
00:44:53,040 --> 00:44:54,180
 Pa okupljanje desnici je nama glavni cijel.

1312
00:44:54,180 --> 00:44:55,220
 Da će baš biti interesantno,

1313
00:44:55,220 --> 00:44:56,020
 hoćete uspjeti to.

1314
00:44:56,020 --> 00:44:57,040
 Ljudi to, recimo,

1315
00:44:57,040 --> 00:44:58,760
 desno-orientirano obidočko tijelo

1316
00:44:58,760 --> 00:45:00,000
 to čekaju već desetlječima.

1317
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:00,600
 Je, je, je.

1318
00:45:00,600 --> 00:45:01,780
 Iako ja moram ovako,

1319
00:45:01,780 --> 00:45:04,560
 ja mislim da čak situacija na desnici

1320
00:45:04,560 --> 00:45:06,020
 nije nikad čak bila ni bolja.

1321
00:45:06,020 --> 00:45:07,780
 Bez obzira šta postoje različite stranke.

1322
00:45:07,780 --> 00:45:09,660
 Sjetite se situacije pri 15 godina.

1323
00:45:09,660 --> 00:45:12,620
 HSP imao jednog zastupnika u saboru

1324
00:45:12,620 --> 00:45:13,340
 i to je bilo to.

1325
00:45:13,340 --> 00:45:16,620
 Nakon toga je i HSP otišao van sabora

1326
00:45:16,620 --> 00:45:18,200
 i vi niste praktički imali ništa.

1327
00:45:18,200 --> 00:45:20,560
 Sad imamo četiri stranke u saboru

1328
00:45:20,560 --> 00:45:21,760
 koje su tesne pravinjencije.

1329
00:45:21,760 --> 00:45:23,020
 Ulaze dvije različite.

1330
00:45:23,160 --> 00:45:24,580
 Znači, mi smo i na prošlijim izborima imali

1331
00:45:24,580 --> 00:45:25,960
 imali smo,

1332
00:45:25,960 --> 00:45:28,780
 s jedne strane smo bili mi suverenisti sa mostom.

1333
00:45:28,780 --> 00:45:34,260
 S druje strane išao je domovinski pokret.

1334
00:45:34,260 --> 00:45:35,780
 Tako da, či, i svi smo ušli u sabor.

1335
00:45:35,780 --> 00:45:38,680
 Tako da, kažem, mislim da se to može

1336
00:45:38,680 --> 00:45:40,860
 još bolje, još više.

1337
00:45:40,860 --> 00:45:44,180
 Mi smo, eto, ostvarili jako dobar uspjeh

1338
00:45:44,180 --> 00:45:45,380
 kao suverenisti u Vukovaru.

1339
00:45:45,380 --> 00:45:47,560
 To je čak i nas iznenadilo

1340
00:45:47,560 --> 00:45:51,400
 s obzirom da smo išli protiv dvije vladajuće stranke

1341
00:45:51,400 --> 00:45:51,980
 koje je tamo...

1342
00:45:51,980 --> 00:45:52,440
 ADZ i DP.

1343
00:45:52,600 --> 00:45:54,000
 ADZ i DP zajedno.

1344
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:55,940
 Naš Marijan Pavličak je uspio

1345
00:45:55,940 --> 00:46:01,500
 dobiti tu bitku za vukovar političku

1346
00:46:01,500 --> 00:46:05,160
 i na neki način tamo ćemo, eto,

1347
00:46:05,160 --> 00:46:07,680
 pokušati pokazati što znamo i što možemo.

1348
00:46:07,680 --> 00:46:11,700
 Znači, gospodin Pavličak se i povukao

1349
00:46:11,700 --> 00:46:13,320
 svoj mandat u saboru,

1350
00:46:13,320 --> 00:46:15,900
 dok se bavi samo i slučivo gradom,

1351
00:46:15,900 --> 00:46:17,460
 jer to je veliki posao.

1352
00:46:17,460 --> 00:46:21,680
 Tako da, to je nešto gdje ćemo se

1353
00:46:22,040 --> 00:46:25,600
 fokusirat, znači, gradnja, organizacija

1354
00:46:25,600 --> 00:46:29,600
 i borba za zajedništvo na desnici.

1355
00:46:29,600 --> 00:46:30,600
 Kako ste u Karlovcu?

1356
00:46:30,600 --> 00:46:31,380
 Moram priznati.

1357
00:46:31,380 --> 00:46:33,520
 U Karlovcu imamo tu,

1358
00:46:33,520 --> 00:46:35,440
 imamo nešto članova,

1359
00:46:35,440 --> 00:46:37,960
 članova, nismo nešto pretjereno jakim,

1360
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:41,480
 išli smo tu zajedno sa mostom na izbore,

1361
00:46:41,480 --> 00:46:43,680
 mislim da je tu naš Ivan Krajcar bio,

1362
00:46:43,680 --> 00:46:44,720
 nosili, ali ste?

1363
00:46:44,720 --> 00:46:45,300
 Da.

1364
00:46:45,300 --> 00:46:48,040
 Nažalost, jako bili smo, ne znam,

1365
00:46:48,040 --> 00:46:51,340
 blizu 5%, što mi je bilo jako žao,

1366
00:46:51,340 --> 00:46:53,780
 ali idemo dalje.

1367
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:55,720
 Tako da, eto, uglavnom,

1368
00:46:55,720 --> 00:46:59,260
 mislim, ja se nadam da ćemo i u Karlovcu imat

1369
00:46:59,260 --> 00:47:01,920
 jednu ovaj dobru organizaciju,

1370
00:47:01,920 --> 00:47:03,560
 da budemo, da imamo neki rezultat,

1371
00:47:03,560 --> 00:47:05,440
 respektabilan, tako da.

1372
00:47:06,100 --> 00:47:08,180
 Možno pravi, spominio si i udrugu Jazovka.

1373
00:47:08,180 --> 00:47:08,440
 Da.

1374
00:47:08,440 --> 00:47:10,080
 Pa možeš nešto već o tome?

1375
00:47:10,080 --> 00:47:11,740
 Pa evo, da, ja sam već

1376
00:47:11,740 --> 00:47:14,400
 nekde godinu i pol dana

1377
00:47:14,400 --> 00:47:15,080
 predsjednik

1378
00:47:15,080 --> 00:47:18,620
 udruge Hrvatski obredni iz drugi Jazovka,

1379
00:47:18,620 --> 00:47:21,720
 uključen sam u njezini rad još od samog početaka.

1380
00:47:21,720 --> 00:47:24,020
 Bio sam puno puta

1381
00:47:24,020 --> 00:47:25,540
 voditelj

1382
00:47:25,540 --> 00:47:27,980
 programa, tamo autor

1383
00:47:27,980 --> 00:47:30,660
 proglasa,

1384
00:47:30,660 --> 00:47:31,420
 pa sam, eto,

1385
00:47:31,420 --> 00:47:33,560
 nekako nekom smjenom generacija

1386
00:47:33,560 --> 00:47:35,240
 došao na čelo

1387
00:47:35,240 --> 00:47:36,460
 udruge.

1388
00:47:36,460 --> 00:47:38,320
 To je jedna ovako

1389
00:47:38,320 --> 00:47:40,600
 tema koja je

1390
00:47:40,600 --> 00:47:42,400
 dosta ovako bolna, znači

1391
00:47:42,400 --> 00:47:45,020
 trebalo se eto koliko 35 godina

1392
00:47:45,020 --> 00:47:45,960
 čekati na

1393
00:47:45,960 --> 00:47:49,160
 iskop posmrtnih ostataka,

1394
00:47:49,160 --> 00:47:50,620
 koji kad je bio i sam iskop

1395
00:47:50,620 --> 00:47:52,480
 se vidilo da ih ima duplo više nego što je

1396
00:47:52,480 --> 00:47:53,500
 što se mislo.

1397
00:47:53,500 --> 00:47:54,440
 814

1398
00:47:54,440 --> 00:47:57,540
 posmrtnih ostataka je izvađeno

1399
00:47:57,540 --> 00:47:59,420
 iz jame Jazovke.

1400
00:47:59,420 --> 00:48:01,460
 Prošle godine u Kolovuzu je bio

1401
00:48:01,460 --> 00:48:02,200
 konačno

1402
00:48:02,200 --> 00:48:03,440
 i

1403
00:48:03,440 --> 00:48:04,880
 pogreb.

1404
00:48:04,880 --> 00:48:07,560
 u

1405
00:48:07,560 --> 00:48:09,640
 zajedničko groblje.

1406
00:48:09,640 --> 00:48:12,420
 Eto, to je nešto,

1407
00:48:12,420 --> 00:48:15,060
 to je neka slika i prilika što se događalo sa,

1408
00:48:15,060 --> 00:48:16,500
 kakav je bio odnos Hrvatske

1409
00:48:16,500 --> 00:48:18,840
 prema žrtavama

1410
00:48:18,840 --> 00:48:20,960
 komunizma

1411
00:48:20,960 --> 00:48:22,960
 u ovih 30 godina.

1412
00:48:22,960 --> 00:48:24,200
 Nitko nije za to odgovarao.

1413
00:48:24,260 --> 00:48:26,000
 u Bojice i Jazovke su bili živi do

1414
00:48:26,000 --> 00:48:27,600
 sredine 2000-tih.

1415
00:48:27,600 --> 00:48:31,520
 Mirno su normalno živjeli,

1416
00:48:31,520 --> 00:48:34,340
 hodali ulicama Hrvatske,

1417
00:48:34,340 --> 00:48:35,580
 znalo se ko su i što su,

1418
00:48:35,580 --> 00:48:37,720
 međutim, niko nije pokretao nikakve

1419
00:48:37,720 --> 00:48:39,640
 unatoč apelima razno raznim.

1420
00:48:39,740 --> 00:48:41,040
 ljudi koji su bili tu prije mene,

1421
00:48:41,040 --> 00:48:43,740
 izjavama svjedoka.

1422
00:48:43,740 --> 00:48:47,440
 Mislim da je vozač,

1423
00:48:47,440 --> 00:48:52,560
 ima ona snimka na YouTube-u gdje je vozač koji je vozio te ljude na odstrel.

1424
00:48:53,420 --> 00:48:55,740
 dočio, spominje konkretna imena,

1425
00:48:55,740 --> 00:48:56,300
 Drago Rafa.

1426
00:48:56,300 --> 00:48:57,380
 Kako radi savjest kad tato.

1427
00:48:57,380 --> 00:48:57,580
 Da.

1428
00:48:57,580 --> 00:49:00,100
 I tako dalje.

1429
00:49:00,100 --> 00:49:00,680
 Uglavnom,

1430
00:49:00,680 --> 00:49:04,540
 eto, ja nastojim koliko je u mojoj moći

1431
00:49:04,540 --> 00:49:08,060
 da se to ne zatre,

1432
00:49:08,060 --> 00:49:09,500
 da ta istina,

1433
00:49:09,500 --> 00:49:12,700
 barem taj jedan dan, eto,

1434
00:49:12,700 --> 00:49:14,480
 evo taj dan.

1435
00:49:14,480 --> 00:49:17,180
 Mi na Jazovci imamo komemoraciju 22. lipnja.

1436
00:49:17,180 --> 00:49:19,900
 Dan takozvane antifašističke borbe.

1437
00:49:19,900 --> 00:49:22,820
